comments: Huerter (SAC) is turning slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Curry's (GSW) side during the drive.
Wiggins (GSW) engages and disengages with Barnes (SAC), and marginal contact occurs as they approach the screen.
Huerter (SAC) is firming up over his right foot and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen on Wiggins (GSW).
Wiggins (GSW) is established in Barnes' (SAC) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs prior to further marginal arm contact taking place as Barnes backs Wiggins down in the post.
Green (GSW) grasps and then quickly releases Sabonis' (SAC) right arm after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Murray's (SAC) left hand comes outward prior to marginal contact occurring with Curry's (GSW) front as Curry crosses over on the perimeter.
Kuminga (GSW) brings his right arm to Huerter's (SAC) upper half and quickly disengages as marginal contact occurs.
Huerter (SAC) establishes himself in Kuminga's (GSW) path and absorbs the initial contact to his upper body prior to further marginal lower body contact occurring during the pick.
Green (GSW) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with Fox's (SAC) upper body prior to the start of Fox's upward shooting motion.
Sabonis (SAC) brings his hands forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Wiggins' (GSW) side as the pick is set.
Wiggins' (GSW) left forearm slightly extends toward Sabonis' (SAC) front and marginal contact occurs as they each elevate for the rebound.
Fox (SAC) firms up over his right foot in Curry's (GSW) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs prior to Murray (SAC) cleanly blocking the driving shot attempt.
Murray (SAC) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Murray (SAC) jumps forward slightly with his forearm brought toward Kuminga's (GSW) left side and marginal contact occurs as Kuminga finishes at the rim.
Curry (GSW) slightly extends forward prior to marginal body contact occurring with Fox (SAC) during the drive.
Curry (GSW) retreats his right forearm away from Fox's (SAC) front as Fox starts his upward shooting motion and marginal contact occurs.
Sabonis (SAC) has a grasp of Green's (GSW) right arm and marginal contact occurs prior to Sabonis back-tapping the rebound toward the perimeter.

Murray (SAC) brings his left arm outward as he jumps toward the sideline and marginal contact occurs with Wiggins' (GSW) face when Murray saves the ball back into play. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Wiggins (GSW) brings his hands toward Murray's (SAC) side and marginal contact occurs as Murray jumps toward the sideline to save the ball back into play.
Murray (SAC) grasps and then quickly releases Wiggins' (GSW) jersey during the rebound.

Sabonis (SAC) follows through after attempting to reach the loose ball and contact occurs with Curry's (GSW) head/face.  Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.

Murray (SAC) raises both arms up to pursue the rebound and he makes clean contact with the ball prior to marginal contact occurring with Wiggins' (GSW) face. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Curry's (GSW) back is out of bounds on the baseline when he gains control of the ball.
Sabonis (SAC) establishes himself in Curry's (GSW) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen.
Curry (GSW) establishes himself in Barnes' (SAC) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen during the inbound.
Kuminga (GSW) lifts and re-plants his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Barnes (SAC) is retreating in Kuminga's (GSW) path and absorbs the marginal contact that occurs as Kuminga turns toward the basket before starting his upward shooting motion.

Sabonis' (SAC) left arm comes forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Kuminga's (GSW) left arm during Kuminga's upward shooting motion. Barnes (SAC) then cleanly blocks Kuminga's layup attempt prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Kuminga (GSW) commits a take foul on Huerter (SAC).
Barnes (SAC) and Wiggins (GSW) make incidental arm contact with one another prior to Barnes back-tapping the ball toward the perimeter during the rebound.
Huerter (SAC) makes incidental contact with Thompson (GSW) as Thompson secures the rebound.
Curry's (GSW) off-arm slightly extends forward toward Huerter's (SAC) front and marginal contact occurs as Curry releases away toward the sideline.
Fox (SAC) avoids making contact with Curry (GSW) prior to Curry losing control of the ball on his own.
